 <br><br>Belfast Live and Mirror NI have once again united as media partners for CHSq at the iconic Custom House Square in Belfast. The stage saw international acts like Becky Hill, Belters Only, and Kodaline perform. The Festival partnership season ended with a 2-day dance music festival called Emerge where thousands showed up to watch some of the biggest dance music artists in the world. With prominent branding and activations, it was another incredibly successful year
