In Belfast, Reach sponsored a prestigious prize at the 2023 Annual Awards held by Ulster University's School of Communication and Media. The recipient of this award was Berni Neill, Strategic Segment Marketing Manager at Calor Gas, who achieved the highest grade average at Diploma level in the esteemed Postgraduate Programme in Digital Marketing Communication & Leadership.
