              <p style="color: #3D5161;font-family: Tahoma;">CReach has joined forces with Oxfam for their Secondhand September campaign. Starting now, our staff can contribute by bringing in clothes they no longer need and placing them in the designated Oxfam bin. This bin is conveniently located on the Commercial side of the Dublin Hub, right beside the photocopier and in the kitchen within the Belfast Hub.At the end of the month, Reach will organise the transfer of the clothes to local Oxfam shops. This initiative encourages individuals to purchase secondhand items while promoting mindful consumption that benefits both people and the planet. 
